name: v21-native-curried-fold-left
---

# Curried collection fold

```scalascript
def runningTotals(xs: List[Int]): List[Int] =
  xs.foldLeft(List[Int]()) { (acc, value) =>
    val previous = if acc.isEmpty then 0 else acc.last
    acc ++ List(previous + value)
  }

def arrayTotal(xs: Any): Int =
  xs.foldLeft(0)((acc, value) => acc + value)

println(runningTotals(List(1, 2, 3, 4, 5)).mkString(", "))
println(arrayTotal(Array(1, 2, 3, 4)))
```
